## RAV Protocol

The **RAV Protocol** (Real Asset Verification Protocol) — the dual-AI
consensus mechanism combining Grok (xAI) and Google Gemini for on-chain
agricultural asset valuation — is an original design of the Solaris CET Team.

As of the copyright date above, **no patent applications** have been filed for
the RAV Protocol or any other component of this Software. The Solaris CET Team
has chosen to make the RAV Protocol available under the MIT License and
contributes it to the public domain of open-source software.

Should patent applications be filed in the future, the Solaris CET Team
commits to providing a royalty-free patent license to all users of the
Software consistent with the terms of this grant.

