## DCBM Model

The **DCBM** (Distributed Circular Block Model) tokenomics model, which
governs the 9,000 CET fixed supply, 90-year emission schedule, and
hyper-scarcity mechanics implemented in this repository, is an original
contribution of the Solaris CET Team and is likewise contributed under the
MIT License with no reserved patent rights.

